snippet.title: Call of Duty®: Black Ops III Zombies Chronicles Story Trailer
snippet.description:
Relive the story of the undead in Call of Duty®: Black Ops III Zombies Chronicles, the ultimate remastered Zombies collection from Treyarch, creators of the original Call of Duty Zombies saga.  

Call of Duty®: Black Ops III Zombies Chronicles arrives first on PS4 on May 16th. 

Pre-order today and get the Zombies Chronicles PS4 Dynamic Theme: https://www.callofduty.com/zombieschronicles

Follow us for the latest intel: 
Web: http://www.callofduty.com
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/CallofDuty and https://www.facebook.com/Treyarch
Twitter: https://twitter.com/CallofDuty and https://twitter.com/Treyarch
Instagram: https://instagram.com/callofduty and https://instagram.com/treyarch
Snapchat: callofduty
